outputs.output_descr: This project seeks to enhance the climate resilience of coastal areas’ economic, natural and social systems of the communities by strengthening policies, institutions and individuals mandated to manage coastal areas.

project_descr: This project is centered on a common goal of achieving sustainable development through improved environmental management and based on Coastal / marines ecosystems preservation.
project_title: Enhancing Resilence of Vulnerable Coastal Areas & Commun
